The Inter-Fraternity Council (IFC) serves as the coordinating body for Alpha Gamma Rho, Sigma Pi, Phi Mu Alpha Sinfonia, and Alpha Kappa Lambda Colony. The council stands for leadership and chivalry, as well as promoting healthy recruitment and enriching growth through brotherhood. IFC serves to provide leadership and guidance to the IFC fraternities. The Inter-Fraternity Council endlessly pursues the ongoing development of high academic standards, philanthropic opportunities, and inter-fraternity unity.
